{"tid":1586524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉車廂非禮女乘客　休班港鐵車長拒認罪保釋11月審","createTime":"2019-09-22T04:03:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T04:03:45.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4a34437c2901456cbcdab78ff05756d5f5d3ed6b","tid":1586524,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:03:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/09/facebook_500x262__2019092016174666544_popup.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F09%2Ffacebook_500x262__2019092016174666544_popup.jpg&h=09d78921&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港鐵油塘站。 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<strong>事主通知車站控制室派員協助</strong><br />\n<br />\n31歲港鐵車長疑於本年六月，休班搭乘列車時非禮一名女乘客，期後兩人於油塘站下車報警求助，警方調查後拘捕涉案車長，被控以一項非禮罪，被告今於觀塘裁判法院否認控罪，裁判官將案件押後至11月19日開審，期間被告獲准保釋外出。<br />\n<br />\n被告劉韋辛被控於本年6月19日在觀塘港鐵鰂魚涌站往油塘站列車非禮女子X。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，當晚約9時許，25歲女子X在港鐵油塘站三號月台使用召援服務，通知車站控制室派員協助，車站職員到場後，X指控劉在之前同一列將軍澳線寶琳方向的列車上涉嫌非禮，並報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/5114776-%E6%B6%89%E8%BB%8A%E5%BB%82%E9%9D%9E%E7%A6%AE%E5%A5%B3%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2-%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E8%BB%8A%E9%95%B7%E6%8B%92%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B11%E6%9C%88?current_cat=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F5114776-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%25BB%2582%25E9%259D%259E%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E4%25B9%2598%25E5%25AE%25A2-%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%258F%25AD%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E8%25BB%258A%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%258B%2592%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E5%2587%2586%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B11%25E6%259C%2588%3Fcurrent_cat%3D3&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FQsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=877eb34c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/5114776-%E6%B6%89%E8%BB%8A%E5%BB%82%E9%9D%9E%E7%A6%AE%E5%A5%B3%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2-%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E8%BB%8A%E9%95%B7%E6%8B%92%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B11%E6%9C%88?current_cat=3</a>"}]}